            "description": "As chair of Young Shell Rijswijk Social Committee I served as  ambassador for the Young Shell network regarding its reputation, vision, planning and budget in order to meet the D&I targets. \nThe chair of the Young Shell Rijswijk committee is the primary focal point for any stakeholders regarding Young Shell-Rijswijk matters. Primary responsibilities involved are: \nChair meetings of Young Shell Rijswijk Social committee (Bi-weekly)\nSupport your committee members \nMaintain professionalism and reputation of Young Shell in and outside of Shell\nVision, and plan of social activities and major flagship events (Joint monthly drinks with Young Shell The Hague, other non-alcoholic activities) \nBudget planning (with treasurer of YSR): discuss budget with sponsor and communicate to team\nProvide support to committee members and interact with other committees\nPlan budget for events, generate ideas for \nAmongst other activites I was also responsible for participating and subsequently leading a team to frame and organise the Young Shell Rijswijk Pubquiz  where I was the quizmaster leading the event 3 years in a row.\n"
